    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Strap In, Guardian: The Acclaimed Hyper-Speed Roguelite Explodes into VR!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The &quot;Overwhelmingly Positive&quot; rated flatscreen roguelite is here, specially rebuilt for VR, Roboquest VR delivers the fastest, most fluid, and deepest roguelite FPS in VR, period.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151760/extras/f1ff5585f3de53bcbfd009335031bd8d.poster.avif?t=1768492309\" width=1170 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151760/extras/f1ff5585f3de53bcbfd009335031bd8d.webm?t=1768492309\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151760/extras/f1ff5585f3de53bcbfd009335031bd8d.mp4?t=1768492309\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >TOP FEATURES:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚡ BLISTERING HYPER-MOBILITY</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔫 INSANE ARSENAL &amp; TACTILE COMBAT</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🛠️ DEEP ROGUELITE CUSTOMIZATION</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >♾️ ENDLESS CHAOS</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💥 VIBRANT CEL-SHADED APOCALYPSE</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🤝 2-PLAYER &quot;BROBOT&quot; CO-OP (COMING SOON)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151760/extras/6e1b5c6435d1d9af5c4222142221c261.poster.avif?t=1768492309\" width=1170 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151760/extras/6e1b5c6435d1d9af5c4222142221c261.webm?t=1768492309\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151760/extras/6e1b5c6435d1d9af5c4222142221c261.mp4?t=1768492309\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The World is Broken. Time to Reboot It.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the metallic boots of a rebooted Guardian and dive headfirst into a fast-paced, roguelite FPS experience like no other. With intuitive VR controls, you'll feel every shot, every dodge, and every exhilarating moment as you battle hordes of robots. Team up with a brobot and save the world!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feel the most kinetic combat available in a headset as you sprint, slide, and grind across scorched canyons and futuristic cities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Total Immersion:</i> Physically weave through bullet hell, dodge incoming plasma fire with your own body, and return the favor with pinpoint precision.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Fluid, High-Octane Action:</i> The movement is buttery-smooth, the combat is explosive, and the action never stops.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151760/extras/2dc79b4c4bcf767e1ffb3d67ed8aad43.poster.avif?t=1768492309\" width=1170 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151760/extras/2dc79b4c4bcf767e1ffb3d67ed8aad43.webm?t=1768492309\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151760/extras/2dc79b4c4bcf767e1ffb3d67ed8aad43.mp4?t=1768492309\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unleash an Insane Arsenal</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your fingertips are the trigger. Every run is a new experiment in devastation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Visceral Firepower:</i> Feel the kick of high-powered shotguns, physically draw back a high-tension bow, or shred bots up close with razor-sharp melee weapons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Master Your Tools:</i> Utilize interactive weapon handling and manual reloading to stay in the fight. Mix and match your loadout and turn the robotic legion into molten slag.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Chaos Never Repeats</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blast through levels that shift and evolve with dynamically generated enemy encounters. The bots adapt, and so must you. Discover hidden secrets, face down colossal bosses, and uncover the mysteries of a long-forgotten civilization.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151760/extras/432b40745fd119124e8d6dc4069e6d9a.poster.avif?t=1768492309\" width=1170 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151760/extras/432b40745fd119124e8d6dc4069e6d9a.webm?t=1768492309\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151760/extras/432b40745fd119124e8d6dc4069e6d9a.mp4?t=1768492309\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Are you fast enough, Guardian?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
